        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Ring 1</P><P>What you need: <BR>Level 50, high warmly faction (100 points below ally, 1000 points in absolute terms.)</P><P>Give Herald Telcha in Chardok two Mt. Death mineral salts or a green goblin skin and then say, "I serve the sarnak". You will be rewarded with: </P><P><b>Di`Zok Signet of Service (ac2 1cha 1int 1wis 65hp 45mana LORE NO DROP)</b></P><P><BR>Ring 2</P><P>What you need: <BR>Ally faction, Ring 1, The head of Warlord Skargus, Drogan Warlord's Insignia</P><P>1. Talk to "a goblin traitor" (2-3 hour spawn) in Droga at 0, -175 and say "what evidence". He will give you a note.</P><P>2. Take this note to "a Sarnak spy" in Frontier Mountains at 1880, 3600. Follow the dialogue and you will eventually say, "I will get the report." He will give you a forged note.</P><P>3. Take this forged note to "a shady goblin" in Warsilik Woods near Cabilis at –1645, -1135 on the 2nd floor, along with a Drogan Warlord's Insignia (random drop in Nurga.) He will give you the "report."</P><P>4. Take this report to "an angry goblin" (5 day spawn) in Droga at 150, 1950. This will spawn Warlord Skargus (level 56 SK with a 1k HT). Kill Skargus and loot head.</P><P>5. Take ring #1 and the head back to Herald Telcha in Chardok and he will reward you with: </P><P><b>Regal Band of Bathezid<BR>(ac5 2cha 2int 2wis 5sta 85hp 50mana, 5 charges of 25point ds LORE NODROP)</b></P><P><BR>Cords Quest</P><P>What you need:<BR>Ally faction<BR>Undead Dragon Sinew (Trakanon, Juggs)<BR>Urn of Spirits (Drusilla Sathir)<BR>Ring 2 </P><P>Hand Undead Dragon Sinew, Urn of Spirits and Ring 2 to Queen in Chardok. You get ring 2 back and the cord.</P><P><b>Spirit Wracked Cord (Lore, No Drop)<BR>Shoulder, Arms, Wrist<BR>AC12, Sta5, Hp100, SvCold+10, SvMagic+5<BR>Effect: Aura of Battle (regen for 2 hps per tick and +10 atk)<BR>All/All Weight 0.0</b></P><P> </font></td>

